org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections

クラス RedisProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>
      • java.util.Hashtable<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>
        • java.util.Properties
          • org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections.RedisProperties
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentMap<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>, java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>, RedisMap<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>, RedisStore

    public class RedisProperties
extends java.util.Properties
implements RedisMap<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>
    Properties extension for a Redis back-store. Useful for reading (and storing) properties inside a Redis hash. Particularly useful inside a Spring container for hooking into Spring's property placeholder or org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertiesFactoryBean.

    Note that this implementation only accepts Strings - objects of other type are not supported.

    作成者:
    Costin Leau
    関連項目:
    Properties, org.sxb.io.support.PropertiesLoaderSupport, 直列化された形式
